  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CSecurity Attack +1\uFF1E \n\uFF1CIce Clad\uFF1E (This
    Digimon compares its number of digivolution cards instead of DP in battles other
    than with security Digimon)\n[When Digivolving] Trash any 4 digivolution cards
