    cards, return 1 of your opponent's Tamers to the bottom of the deck.\n[Opponent's
    Turn] None of your opponent's Digimon with as many or fewer digivolution cards
    as this Digimon can suspend.\n[Rule] Trait: Has the [Ice-Snow] type."
